Seminar: Feminist Clickback - Search Engine Optimization (SEO) against the far-right

7. Oktober 2017, 13-17h, in NFJ Laden, Weichselstraße 13/14, 12045 Berlin

Part of the Naturfreundejugend Berlin program

In this seminar we will present Search Engine Optimization (SEO) and discuss how we can use this knowledge to bring feminist content to a wider audience.
This seminar is meant for anyone who is interested, and also people who as part of their political work already have or are planning a website/blog.
